snippet.title: Barbie Groom and Glam Pups Trailer (Wii & DS)
snippet.description:
http://www.everybodyplays.co.uk/games/DS/Barbie-Groom-and-Glam-Pups/693
Barbie Groom and Glam Pups lets you choose a pup from one of six adorable breeds, then groom it, train it, and dress it up. Finally, you get to show off your glam pup in a fabulous dance sequence, runway show and photo shoot!
